high_descs: Turn around and go near the shelf.
Take the credit card from the shelf.

Put the credit cart near the floor lamp and it will be glow.

high_descs: Head straight towards the shelf by turning around and turning left.

Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the floor lamp.

high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the shelf.
Pick the credit card from the shelf.
Turn right to the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a credit card by the light of a tall lamp.
